主体人工文字/主体人工文字_0039.jpg.mt:
More蓬松and more弹性than the silk quilt with no elasticity and weight-increasing treatment!

Friendly reminder:

There are silk quilts on the market with very poor fluffiness and elasticity, which have been treated for weight increase. Silk is sold based on its weight.

Some unscrupulous merchants illegally use silk floss to increase the weight. A 4-jin silk quilt may only contain 3 jin of silk, with the remaining 1 jin being a lubricating oil-based chemical weight-increasing agent adsorbed on the silk fibers. After testing, the amino acid content of basic proteins is seriously substandard.
src: 比无弹性的增重处理的蚕丝被
更有蓬松性 更有弹性！
友情提醒：市场上有蓬松度弹性很差的蚕丝被，有增重处理，蚕丝都是按蚕丝重量卖的，现有不法商家违法使用丝绵增重处理，可能4斤的蚕丝被，只有3斤的蚕丝，余下1斤是吸附在蚕丝纤维上的润滑油性化学增重剂。
经检测，基蛋白质氨基酸含量严重不达标。
